comments: Durant (PHX) brings his off-arm slightly forward and marginal contact occurs as Durant (PHX) releases away to enter his upward shooting motion.
Durant (PHX) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it away from Barnes (TOR) prior to incidental arm to body contact occurring during the drive.
Siakam (TOR)  extends both arms and initiates contact with Okogie (PHX) that impedes his ability to pursue the rebound.
Poeltl (TOR) is imminently exiting the lane within three seconds.
Nurkic (PHX) makes incidental hand-on-ball contact to block Siakam's (TOR) shot attempt near the rim.
Nurkic (PHX) firms up over his right foot in Anunoby's (TOR) path and marginal contact occurs as the pick is set.
Poeltl (TOR) clamps and holds Nurkic's (PHX) arm, which affects his ability to pursue the rebound.
Nurkic (PHX) moves alongside Schroder's (TOR) path and marginal body contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Achiuwa (TOR) legally contests Durant's (PHX) jump shot attempt.
Goodwin (PHX) commits a take foul on Schroder (TOR). The transition take foul rule does not apply to the last two minutes of either the fourth quarter or overtime.
Gordon (PHX) attempts to go for the steal and initiates contact with Barnes' (TOR) arm.

There is not clear and conclusive angle confirming this play. From available angles, it appears that Barnes (TOR) deflects the ball from Durant (PHX) as he's dribbling, and after the ball hits Durant's leg, Barnes touches it again before it goes out of bounds.
Siakam (TOR) moves alongside Goodwin (PHX) and marginal body contact occurs during Goodwin's layup attempt.
